                                    oc:codeContent """## Converting to PDF

### From Word
**Settings**:
- [ ] Embed fonts
- [ ] Include bookmarks
- [ ] Set PDF/A for archival
- [ ] Compress images (optional)

### From Excel
**Settings**:
- [ ] Define print area
- [ ] Set page breaks
- [ ] Choose orientation
- [ ] Fit to page options

### From PowerPoint
**Settings**:
- [ ] Slide range
- [ ] Include notes (optional)
- [ ] Quality level
- [ ] Handout format (optional)

### Universal Tips
1. Review in print preview first
2. Check page breaks
3. Ensure fonts are embedded
4. Verify hyperlinks work
""" ;
